I'll look into it and tell you all later.

1058
01:01:57,816 --> 01:01:59,306
ありがとね。ややこしいぞ、わかる。
Thanks. It is confusing, I know.

1059
01:01:59,306 --> 01:02:01,486
ということで、それじゃあみんな、また、おつかなたー！
Well then, everyone, see you later, Otsukanata!

1060
01:02:01,486 --> 01:02:03,806
